    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy支持与特朗普的友好电话中的停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-says-ukraine-talks-on-track-after-zelenskiy-putin-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统沃罗迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）同意一项提议，以阻止能源资产罢工，这是唐纳德·特朗普总统在三年前俄罗斯全面入侵始于俄罗斯全面入侵开始的战争的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-says-ukraine-talks-on-track-after-zelenskiy-putin-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 15:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党人向教职员工名单，道德政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/house-democrats-ask-doge-to-produce-staffer-list-ethics-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院民主党人正在敦促唐纳德·特朗普总统政府效率部门，以提高透明度，以解决亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）努力减少政府规模和范围的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/house-democrats-ask-doge-to-produce-staffer-list-ethics-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 15:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将1.75亿美元冻结给宾夕法尼亚州的跨性别运动员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-freezes-175-million-to-penn-over-transgender-athletes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫称，特朗普政府已将1.75亿美元的联邦资金冻结给宾夕法尼亚大学，理由是允许跨性别运动员参加妇女体育运动的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-freezes-175-million-to-penn-over-transgender-athletes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国土安全部削减员工领导与国内极端主义的斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据现任和前官员的说法，特朗普政府对美国政府工人的清除局势摧毁了一个旨在打击在线激进化的国土安全部门，并认为在过去几年中有助于破坏1000多个暴力地块。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由特朗普政府解雇的民主联邦法院委员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-administration-dismisses-two-democratic-ftc-commissioners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府驳回了美国联邦贸易委员会上的两名民主党人，白宫对美国机构的控制权进行了最新行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-administration-dismisses-two-democratic-ftc-commissioners</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 21:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
